"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Time is the most important factor when it comes down to ads and sponsorships. Brave’s “sponsored image” shows up once you open the browser \\\\~ keeping that in mind we should consider the fact that we have a very **limited** amount of time before the said Brave user opens a new tab.\\n\\nThis should give us around **2-15 seconds** and that is the time we have to get their attention which is very limited, therefore we need an *eye-catching* ad that either hooks them or delivers our message very *efficiently*. Taking all that into consideration \\\\~ all signs lead to a **minimalistic art** design that delivers the most in a very limited amount of time.\\n\\nHumans are curious creatures and successful minimal ads focus on capitalizing on that by using **icons** and **very little information**. We can take 3 different approaches:\\n\\n1. Iconic glasses\\n2. Iconic glasses + keywords\\n3. Visual storytelling + keywords\\n\\n![1. Giving nothing away.](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/b50fkrqkIlfFBi4cEjpEc.jpg?height=1440&width=2560)\\n\\n![2. Using keywords and leading the users to the website.](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/OmDE3K9vmt6rMHRlYICMx.jpg?height=1440&width=2560)\\n\\n![2. Creating a small exercise which will challenge the viewer to check out all the words before moving on.](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/2pRWd--iWTUtA6F4RuCPj.jpg?height=1440&width=2560)\\n\\n![2. Creating the \\\"George Orwell effect\\\" as I'd like to call it, by differentiating Nouns from what seems to be the \\\"typical\\\" look of the \\\"others\\\".](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/XiR79cDR5b_VmCe2Sd0Rm.jpg?height=1440&width=2560)\\n\\n![3. 1/3 of Web3 series \\\\~ self-expression](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/CMgOKtdl9dAWQSFFqOi0j.jpg?height=1440&width=2560)\\n\\n![3. 2/3 of Web3 series \\\\~ decentralized community](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/2onc4t4sw3SsxPSJJ97Fo.jpg?height=1440&width=2560)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/jVAaSFiyiBVpZAlAKKMsT.jpg?height=1440&width=2560)\\n\\n\",\"timestamp\":1635204383,\"title\":\"NounsDAO - Brave Takeover Art\"},\"digest\":\"i_2odjm16cDhXgNUXuQ4IPf9G89mlvVmNMI1Q9JMN3g\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x4709B84407DD559C08764fd5dC25bf842b001893\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"3JTgXmSsZqHF5RvIIHAPhQgsW40jsSIePUx0BDw3KCc\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"FZ-mKJKIL7FUMaA_2VGtY30OcRkF9y5JilGePN-BjdI\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"VI-EuYhiJxFYclhTJn52hWeBc4gVk_MqQQIz5EqoIH_jfIs0LEknZ0worLXJtUbh0_zazsD2jYzNL92jtxqRlw\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xeb1cc38209fa76b315b68e378b52e659012a993f8974c7919a19b87c70951a871e83ddf4b67c4a47b14b431f3bd2dc9bd6100ea1f9fc56889410d071765f048e1b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"3JTgXmSsZqHF5RvIIHAPhQgsW40jsSIePUx0BDw3KCc\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"FZ-mKJKIL7FUMaA_2VGtY30OcRkF9y5JilGePN-BjdI\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"qGApL7Z5Ij1qCPlzUnlJ-9eLzFkPbX2Dh10G6nU39_Y\"}"